            "creation_date": 1325116770,
            "body": "<p>ZeroMQ - <a href=\"http://www.zeromq.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.zeromq.org/<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>Although this is a transport layer, it can be tailored for event handling.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 8662680,
