            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1326287879,
            "creation_date": 1326287879,
            "body": "<p>Take a look at akka (http://akka.io/). It offers a distributed actor model in the same vein as erlang for the JVM with both java and scala APIs. <\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 8819943,
            "question_id": 181225
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0a48e6c6557d881db827c642d4c41361?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 4559992,
