            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 2.5",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1223916852,
            "creation_date": 1223916852,
            "body": "<p>If a <a href=\"http://activemq.apache.org/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JMS implementation<\/a> isn't for you, then you may be interested in an <a href=\"http://xmpp.org/about/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">XMPP<\/a> approach. There are multiple implementations, and also have a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Publish/subscribe\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Publish-Subscribe<\/a> <a href=\"http://xmpp.org/tech/pubsub.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">extension<\/a>. <\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 198255,
            "question_id": 181225
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/aa1db08e3d9d4fe6d634095c319ede40?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 46830,
